            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 5,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 40
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "明且達也。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "heshanggong-18",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 5,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 40
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "如闇昧也。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "heshanggong-19",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 5,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 40
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "察察，急且疾也。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "heshanggong-20",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 5,
            "start": 35,
            "end": 36
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "悶悶，無所割截。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "heshanggong-21",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 5,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 40
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "我獨忽忽，如江海之流，莫知其所窮極也。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "heshanggong-22",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 5,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 40
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "我獨漂漂，若飛若揚，無所止也，志意在神域也。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "heshanggong-23",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 7,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 1
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "以，有為也。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "heshanggong-24",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 7,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 23
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "我獨無為。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "heshanggong-25",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 7,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 23
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "鄙，似若不逮也。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "heshanggong-26",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 7,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 23
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "我獨與人異也。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "heshanggong-27",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 7,
            "start": 19,
            "end": 20
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "食，用也。母，道也。我獨貴用道也。",
          "source": "cham"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "wangbi",
      "label": "王弼註",
      "shortLabel": "王",
      "contributor": "C001",
      "role": "commentator",
      "nature": "commentary",
      "displayOrder": 2,
      "enabled": true,
      "annotations": [
        {
          "id": "wangbi-1",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 0,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 19
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "下篇，為學者日益，為道者日損。然則學求益所能，而進其智者也，若將無欲而足，何求於益。不知而中，何求於進。夫燕雀有匹，鳩鴿有仇，寒鄉之民，必知旃裘，自然已足，益之則憂。故續鳧之足，何異截鶴之脛，畏譽而進，何異畏刑。唯阿美惡，相去何若？故人之所畏，吾亦畏焉，未敢恃之以為用也。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "wangbi-2",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 0,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 19
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "歎與俗相返之遠也。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "wangbi-3",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 0,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 19
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "眾人迷於美進，惑於榮利，欲進心競，故熙熙如享太牢，如春登臺也。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "wangbi-4",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 0,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 19
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "言我廓然無形之可名、無兆之可舉，如嬰兒之未能孩也。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "wangbi-5",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 0,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 19
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "若無所宅。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "wangbi-6",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 0,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 19
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "眾人無不有懷有志，盈溢胸心，故曰，皆有餘也。我獨廓然無為無欲，若遺失之也。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "wangbi-7",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 0,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 19
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "絕愚之人，心無所別析，意無所好欲，猶然其情不可覩我頹然若此也。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "wangbi-8",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 0,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 19
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "無所別析，不可為明。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "wangbi-9",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 0,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 19
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "耀其光也。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "wangbi-10",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 0,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 19
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "分別別析也。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "wangbi-11",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 0,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 19
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "情不可覩。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "wangbi-12",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 0,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 19
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "無所繫縶。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "wangbi-13",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 7,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 1
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "以，用也。皆欲有所施用也。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "wangbi-14",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 7,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 23
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "無所欲為，悶悶昏昏，若無所識，故曰頑且鄙也。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "wangbi-15",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 7,
            "start": 0,
            "end": 23
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "食母，生之本也。人者皆棄生民之本，貴末飾之華，故曰我獨欲異於人。",
          "source": "cham"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "source": {
    "textRef": "laozi-boshu",
    "relation": "section"
  }
}